<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.1.3">
<l>kuḻalniṟa vaṇṇaniṉ kūṟukoṇṭa</l>
<l>taḻalniṟa vaṇṇaṉaṇ ṇārnakaram</l>
<l>viḻanaṉi malaicilai vaḷaivuceytaṅ</l>
<l>kaḻalniṟa vampatu vāṉavaṉē</l>
<l rend="indent">āṇṭāyuṉaik kāṇpatō raruḷeṉak karuḷutiyēl,</l>
<l rend="indent">vēṇṭēṉmaṉai vāḻkkaiyai viṇṇakar mēyavaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You the hue of the [blue] kuḻal [fish],</l>
<l rend="indent">the one who became the fire-hued arrow,</l>
<l>Creating a fabrication of a bow from a great mountain,</l>
<l>There when the city of the enemy of the fire-hued one,</l>
<l>Who has a part of you, fell,</l>
<l rend="indent">Master, if you bless me with the one blessing of seeing you,</l>
<l rend="indent">I would not want this domestic life, you who dwells in Viṇṇakar.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
